===Medals by summer sport===

Chinese athletes have won medals in most of the current [[Olympic sports#Summer Olympics|Summer Olympics sports]].<br/>
The exceptions are '''[[Triathlon at the Summer Olympics|triathlon]]''', '''[[Equestrian at the Summer Olympics|equestrian]]''' and '''[[Water polo at the Summer Olympics|water polo]]'''.

