===Medals by winter sport===

Chinese athletes have won medals in only 5 out of 15 current [[Olympic sports#Winter Olympics|Winter Olympics sports]].<br/>
Most of the golds and half of the medals come from the sport of '''[[Short track speed skating at the Winter Olympics|short track speed skating]]'''.

